The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Business | US firm buys Ontrack Solutions
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       US firm buys Ontrack Solutions
          OUR CORRESPONDENT                               
	Mumbai, May 23: New York Stock Exchange-listed Avnet Technology Solutions has acquired Mumbai-based systems integrator Ontrack Solutions for an undisclosed sum.         
	The transaction, which is subject to government approval, is expected to close by mid-July 2008. Ontrack will become part of the operations of Avnet Technology Solutions Asia Pacific.         
	Ontrack Solutions has 160 employees and revenues of $13 million. According to media reports, it supports customers in a variety of end markets such as banking, industrial and manufacturing.         
	We will retain all the employees of Ontrack, while the acquired company will work as a solutions distribution arm of Avnet, said Jaideep Malhotra, Avnet vice-president and general manager (Asia-Pacific).        
	Avnet will leverage Ontracks capabilities to build value-added solutions distribution business. The transaction is expected to be immediately accretive to earnings and supports Avnets long-term return on capital goals.        
	Ontrack is a market leader in security, networking, consolidation, virtualisation, storage and server solutions. Avnet has had a strong presence in India since 1998 through Avnet Electronics Marketing, which is a distributor of electronic components.         
	Avnet Electronics Marketing India has its key office in Bangalore and sales offices in all major locations in the country. It offers a comprehensive line card covering semiconductor, passive, interconnect, and electro-mechanical components.        
	With the acquisition of Ontrack, we are gaining a seasoned management team that shares Avnets commitment to provide value-added solutions to solve business challenges of its customers, said K.P .Tang, president of Avnet Technology Solutions, Asia-Pacific.                                                                                                                                      
